<div class="article-container">

  <h1>Design System</h1>
  <p class="article-excerpt">All visual decisions for this site, in one place. Built with EB Garamond, #FFDC1E, and as little complexity as possible.</p>

  <hr>

  <!-- TYPEFACE -->
  <h2>Typeface</h2>
  <p>Everything — headlines, body, captions — is set in <strong>EB Garamond</strong>. One typeface, all weights, light and dark.</p>

  <div style="margin: var(--space-xl) 0;">
    <p style="font-size: 3rem; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">AaBbCcDdEeFf</p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog</p>
    <p style="font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0; color: var(--color-text-light);">EB Garamond · Regular · Italic · Semibold</p>
  </div>

  <hr>

